## Response Validation

### ✅ Validate LLM output beyond structure:
```python
def validate_test_cases(cases: list[TestCaseDraft]) -> list[TestCaseDraft]:
    """Additional validation beyond Pydantic."""
    validated = []
    
    for case in cases:
        # Ensure steps aren't empty
        if not case.steps or all(not s.strip() for s in case.steps):
            logger.warning("Skipping test case with empty steps: %s", case.title)
            continue
        
        # Ensure title is meaningful
        if len(case.title) < 10:
            logger.warning("Skipping test case with short title: %s", case.title)
            continue
        
        validated.append(case)
    
    return validated
```
